flowchart TD
    Start([User Opens App]) --> Input[Enter Text]
    
    Input --> Validate{Valid?}
    Validate -->|No| ShowError[Show Error]
    ShowError --> Input
    
    Validate -->|Yes| Translate[Click Translate]
    
    Translate --> Loading[Show Loading]
    Loading --> CallAPI[Call API]
    
    CallAPI --> APICheck{Success?}
    APICheck -->|No| Error[Show Error]
    Error --> Input
    
    APICheck -->|Yes| Result[Show Translation]
    
    Result --> Next{Next Action?}
    Next -->|Copy| Copy[Copy Result]
    Next -->|Clear| Input
    Next -->|Done| End([End])
    
    Copy --> Next
    
    style Start fill:#e8f5e9
    style End fill:#ffebee
    style ShowError fill:#fff3e0
    style Error fill:#fff3e0
    style Result fill:#e1f5ff
